text: Great ambience to bring loved ones here. The atmosphere felt like a cruise cafe. Great finger food, the fried chicken wings were well marinated. It's juicy on inside and crispy on outside. It's coffee selection was also wide, and full of flavour. Recommended!

Worst place ever. Asked a young waitress nicely is the seat available or not. She turned around and say "cannot wait ah".... KNN not happy dont work, dont throw tantrum on me. I did nothing to deserve this kind of treatment.
Nice place for gathering with friends, family and couples.. View are good too.
Has a lovely live band and we ordered horfun which was surprisingly good!
Nice quiet pub with nice polite well dressed staff.
